data.description: Nice 3 bedroom, 2 bath with sun room and nice size back yard with inground pool with whirlpool section. Home has vinyl plank flooring through out. Main room has high ceilings and fireplace. Eat in Kitchen also breakfast bar, laundry inside and pull down stairs to attic. Living room, Dining room open floor plan. Split bedrooms with guest rooms in separate hallway. Home is on corner lot with side entry garage. Firepit area pool side stays with the home.  Quiet neighborhood with community beach around the lake. New roof (architectural shingle) with full price offer
